  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To develop practical and effective clinical diagnosis and treatment schemes for the control
      of novel coronavirus pneumonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      By retrospectively analyzing the clinical epidemiological characteristics of the novel
      coronavirus pneumonia and the current diagnosis and treatment schemes, as well as in-depth
      analyzing the disease development process and outcome trends of NCP patients to develop
      practical and effective clinical diagnosis and treatment schemes and provide guarantee for
      the rapid control of the epidemic.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
